{"tid":1741030,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"彈劾案進入白熱化階段，超半數民眾贊成定罪川普","createTime":"2019-11-20T07:08:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T01:09:01.000Z","uid":1086,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"04364e089e273ba8e74054a8ecc186cbe1330f3d","tid":1741030,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:08:41.000Z","msg":"美國眾議院對總統特朗普的彈劾調查繼續推進，第二場公開聽證會美國當地時間周五（11月15日）舉行。前美國駐烏克蘭大使約瓦諾維奇（Marie Yovanovitch）作證時，特朗普實時發表推文，兩人展開隔空辯論。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">第二場公開聽證會上發生了什麼？</span></strong></span><br />\n約瓦諾維奇作證時表示，特朗普在7月與烏克蘭總統通話時稱她為「壞消息」，讓她感到受威脅。<br />\n她還稱，多名白宮官員對她進行抹黑，導致她最終被免職。約瓦諾維奇是資深外交官，職業生涯共33年。<br />\n共和黨人則說，約瓦諾維奇的免職是正常的人事任免。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">美國人支持彈劾特朗普嗎？</span></strong></span><br />\n統計調查網站FiveThirtyEight的估算顯示，美國人在支持還是反對彈劾特朗普的問題上分裂。<br />\n48.5%的美國人支持彈劾特朗普，45.7%的人則持反對意見。隨著通烏門調查的推進，支持彈劾的比例略有上升。<br />\n立場親共和黨的福克斯電視台早前的民意調查亦得出相似的結果，支持彈劾的人數略高於反對一方，但幾乎勢均力敵。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">彈劾調查程序下一步如何發展？</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/F3ED/production/_109654426_trump_impeachment_640_chinese-nc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F624%2Fcpsprodpb%2FF3ED%2Fproduction%2F_109654426_trump_impeachment_640_chinese-nc.png&h=b3724a16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然特朗普彈劾案在參議院通過的概率較低，但民調顯示美國民眾對特朗普越來越不滿。<br />\n ABC數據顯示，51%美國受調者表示特朗普應在國會參議院接受審訊並定罪；另有6%贊成彈劾但不主張將特朗普罷免。<br />\n也就是說，已經超過一半的民眾支持將特朗普定罪，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">這將會嚴重影響到特朗普明年大選的支持率。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"3fab41d00b6f24203166b3d5c658cfe93b6bb9b8","tid":1741030,"uid":79793,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:10:45.000Z","msg":"副總統接班支那玩撚完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b0e2e7a457460df090229243ebc0122fc817648","tid":1741030,"uid":61484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:11:49.000Z","msg":"公字都贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ddf5e1e723b2216420d116c6fc3c79987bb82a4","tid":1741030,"uid":208376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:11:53.000Z","msg":"要投2次票咁過真係有d難<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b55f1fb1d15448417bd3b8dfe80825cd9883ee4","tid":1741030,"uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:13:13.000Z","msg":"投二次票 無咁易"},{"pid":"646cb96130f8e06bd92b372dd30b1d3401616c36","tid":1741030,"uid":1086,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3ddf5e1e723b2216420d116c6fc3c79987bb82a4","tid":1741030,"uid":208376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:11:53.000Z","msg":"要投2次票咁過真係有d難<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:14:01.000Z","msg":"民主黨預左唔會彈劾到<br />\n但搞大左單野,搞到佢下年election就得"},{"pid":"92e2d8a9dc4180a5de378a8ca952214fc2403bd6","tid":1741030,"uid":22694,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3fab41d00b6f24203166b3d5c658cfe93b6bb9b8","tid":1741030,"uid":79793,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:10:45.000Z","msg":"副總統接班支那玩撚完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:14:08.000Z","msg":"Pence軍佬強硬派喎"},{"pid":"779e2c899f34582d7f343f87a9823a5c05e57b9c","tid":1741030,"uid":78383,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:16:07.000Z","msg":"美國人民既反支情緒係重中之重<br />\nBloomberg選到就仆街"},{"pid":"c72c09b6de44e6399b7cf5291dab878ee21ae043","tid":1741030,"uid":199907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"779e2c899f34582d7f343f87a9823a5c05e57b9c","tid":17410